"你距离能够驾驶 %(doctrine)s 还差约 %(levels)s 个技能等级——大约 %(days)s 天的"
"训练——而这正是你的目标 «%(goal)s» 所指向的。依据是你截至 %(as_of)s 的技能。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You are about %(levels)s skill level(s) — roughly %(days)s day(s) — from "
"flying %(doctrine)s, a corp priority-%(priority)s doctrine. Entirely "
"optional — your call."
msgstr ""
"你距离能够驾驶 %(doctrine)s 还差约 %(levels)s 个技能等级——大约 %(days)s 天——"
"它是军团优先级为 %(priority)s 的 doctrine。完全出于自愿，由你决定。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) forms up %(when)s EVE and matches your goal "
"«%(goal)s»."
msgstr ""
"«%(operation)s»（%(op_type)s）将于 EVE 时间 %(when)s 集结，契合你的目标 "
"«%(goal)s»。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(operation)s» (%(op_type)s) forms up %(when)s EVE and matches something "
"you enjoy. Optional — your call."
msgstr ""
"«%(operation)s»（%(op_type)s）将于 EVE 时间 %(when)s 集结，符合你感兴趣的内"
"容。可选参加，由你决定。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(count)s mentor(s) currently cover %(category)s, which matches your goal "
"«%(goal)s». Mentors only ever see what you explicitly share."
msgstr ""
"目前有 %(count)s 位导师负责 %(category)s，与你的目标 «%(goal)s» 相符。导师只"
"能看到你明确选择共享的内容。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(goal)s» hasn't moved in about %(weeks)s week(s). That's completely fine — "
"interests change. If it helps, you could lower its priority, pause it, or "
"adjust the target date."
msgstr ""
"«%(goal)s» 已经大约 %(weeks)s 周没有进展了。这完全没问题——兴趣本就会变化。如"
"果有帮助，你可以调低它的优先级、暂停它，或调整目标日期。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"«%(goal)s» is blocked: %(blockers)s. You can edit the milestone, pick a "
"different doctrine, or keep the goal parked until this resolves — nothing "
"expires."
msgstr ""
"«%(goal)s» 已受阻：%(blockers)s。你可以编辑该里程碑、改选另一套 doctrine，或"
"先把目标搁置，等问题解决——不会有任何内容过期。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid "The corp shipyard can supply a %(ship)s for your goal «%(goal)s»."
msgstr "军团船坞可以为你的目标 «%(goal)s» 提供一艘 %(ship)s。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The corp shipyard can supply a %(ship)s for your goal «%(goal)s». It fits "
"within your configured monthly budget."
msgstr ""
"军团船坞可以为你的目标 «%(goal)s» 提供一艘 %(ship)s。它在你设定的月度预算之"
"内。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Campaign «%(campaign)s» is asking for help: «%(objective)s». This matches "
"your interest in %(activity)s. Volunteering is entirely optional and visible "
"to the campaign team."
msgstr ""
"战役 «%(campaign)s» 正在请求支援：«%(objective)s»。这与你对 %(activity)s 的兴"
"趣相符。报名完全自愿，且对战役团队可见。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"It's been a while since you looked at «%(goal)s». A two-minute review keeps "
"the plan honest — reprioritise, adjust the date, or archive it guilt-free."
msgstr ""
"你已经有一段时间没有查看 «%(goal)s» 了。花两分钟回顾一下，能让计划保持真实——"
"重新排定优先级、调整日期，或者放心地把它归档。"

#: apps/capsuleer/messages.py
msgid ""
"It's been a while since you reviewed your preferences. A quick look keeps "
"your suggestions relevant — update what you enjoy, your pace, or your budget "
"any time."
msgstr ""
"你已经有一段时间没有检查自己的偏好了。快速看一眼，能让推荐保持切题——你随时可"
"以更新自己的兴趣、节奏或预算。"

