msgid "Confirm the cadet submitted a buyback lot."
msgstr "确认学员提交了一笔 buyback 订单。"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a scanning drill with your cadet."
msgstr "和你的学员做一次扫描演练。"

