msgid "Walk through booking a freight contract."
msgstr "演示如何下达一份货运合同。"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain the buyback rates and locations."
msgstr "讲解 buyback 的收购价和收购地点。"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet completed (and ideally ESI-verified) a haul."
msgstr "确认学员完成了一次运输（最好经过 ESI 验证）。"

