msgstr "经由 %(cyno)s 的直接跳跃引擎路线。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so neither the high-sec origin nor the high-sec destination can be "
"reached. Choose a low-sec or null-sec system."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法进入 high-sec（无星门通行权，且 high-sec 内无法点亮 cyno），因"
"此 high-sec 起点和 high-sec 目的地都无法抵达。请选择 low-sec 或 null-sec 星"
"系。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so the high-sec destination can't be reached. Choose a low-sec or null-"
"sec system."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法进入 high-sec（无星门通行权，且 high-sec 内无法点亮 cyno），因此"
"无法抵达 high-sec 目的地。请选择 low-sec 或 null-sec 星系。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't enter high-sec (no stargate access and no cyno in high-"
"sec), so the high-sec origin can't be reached. Choose a low-sec or null-sec "
"system."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法进入 high-sec（无星门通行权，且 high-sec 内无法点亮 cyno），因此"
"无法抵达 high-sec 起点。请选择 low-sec 或 null-sec 星系。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't cyno into or out of high-sec: gate out of the high-sec "
"origin to a low-sec entry, jump, then gate to the high-sec destination."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法用 cyno 进出 high-sec：先从 high-sec 起点走星门到 low-sec 入口，"
"跳跃，然后走星门前往 high-sec 目的地。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't cyno directly into high-sec: jump to a low-sec exit near "
"the destination, then take stargates the rest of the way."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法用 cyno 直接进入 high-sec：先跳跃到目的地附近的 low-sec 出口，剩"
"余路程走星门。"

#: apps/navigation/route_mode.py
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A %(ship)s can't light a cyno in high-sec: gate out of the high-sec origin "
"to a low-sec staging system, then jump from there."
msgstr ""
"%(ship)s 无法在 high-sec 点亮 cyno：先从 high-sec 起点走星门到 low-sec 集结星"
"系，再从那里跳跃。"

