#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Milestone unlocked: First kill!"
msgstr "里程碑达成：首次击杀！"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Congratulations on your first corp killmail! Welcome to the fight."
msgstr "恭喜你拿下第一张军团 killmail！欢迎加入战斗。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Milestone unlocked: First solo kill!"
msgstr "里程碑达成：首次单杀！"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Your first solo kill — you took one down all on your own. Nice work."
msgstr "你的首次单杀 — 完全靠自己击落了一个目标。干得漂亮。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Milestone unlocked: First final blow!"
msgstr "里程碑达成：首次最后一击！"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "You landed your first final blow. The killing shot is yours."
msgstr "你打出了自己的首次最后一击。致命一击归你所有。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Combat rank achieved: {rank_name}"
msgstr "达成战斗军衔：{rank_name}"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Congratulations — you've reached the rank of {rank_name} ({kill_count} "
"lifetime kills recorded). Ranks update from the nightly combat rollup, so "
"this can reflect kills from the last day or two rather than the exact moment."
msgstr ""
"恭喜 — 你已晋升至 {rank_name} 军衔（累计记录 {kill_count} 次击杀）。军衔依据"
"每晚的战斗汇总更新，因此可能反映的是过去一两天的击杀，而非此刻的实时数据。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Congratulations — you've reached the rank of {rank_name} ({kill_count} "
"lifetime kills recorded). A rank reward is pending leadership approval. "
"Ranks update from the nightly combat rollup, so this can reflect kills from "
"the last day or two rather than the exact moment."
msgstr ""
"恭喜 — 你已晋升至 {rank_name} 军衔（累计记录 {kill_count} 次击杀）。军衔报酬"
"正在等待领导层批准。军衔依据每晚的战斗汇总更新，因此这里反映的可能是最近一两"
"天的击杀，而非实时数据。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Trophy unlocked: {trophy_name}"
msgstr "已解锁奖杯：{trophy_name}"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Trophy unlocked: {trophy_name}. {trophy_desc} Trophies update from the "
"killboard's engagement sweep, so this can reflect a kill from the last "
"little while rather than the exact moment."
msgstr ""
"已解锁奖杯：{trophy_name}。{trophy_desc} 奖杯根据 killboard 的交战扫描更新，"
"因此这可能反映的是最近一段时间内的击杀，而非确切时刻。"

