msgstr "本周最佳击杀（{week}）：{value} ISK。在 killboard 上查看。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid "Flying without implants"
msgstr "无植入体飞行"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
msgid ""
"You lost a pod with no implants fitted — no harm done this time. When you're "
"ready, even a cheap set of attribute implants speeds up your skill training. "
"Ask a director for the corp implant guide."
msgstr ""
"您损失了一个未安装任何植入体的 pod——这次没什么损失。当您准备好后，即使是一套"
"廉价的属性植入体也能加快您的技能训练。请向 director 索取军团植入体指南。"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Watchlist tripwire: {entity_name}"
msgstr "关注列表触发预警：{entity_name}"

#: apps/pingboard/messages.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"⚠ Watched {entity_type} **{entity_name}** ({watchlist_name}) was on a "
"killmail in {system_name} ~{minutes}m ago. Risk indicator, not a guarantee — "
"verify before acting."
msgstr ""
"⚠ 被关注的 {entity_type} **{entity_name}**（{watchlist_name}）约 {minutes} 分"
"钟前出现在 {system_name} 的一份 killmail 上。这只是风险提示，并非确证 — 行动"
"前请自行核实。"

