#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/kpis.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/srp.html
#, python-format
msgid "config v%(version)s"
msgstr "配置 v%(version)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#, python-format
msgid "last by %(by)s"
msgstr "最后由 %(by)s 修改"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Calibration — what would be proposed for now"
msgstr "校准 —— 当前会提出哪些提案"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid ""
"No measured outcomes yet — nothing is trusted, so autonomous proposal stays "
"silent even when armed. Trust accrues as accepted COAs complete and their "
"outcomes are measured."
msgstr ""
"尚无已测量的结果 —— 没有任何行动族可信，因此即便已启用，自主提案也会保持静"
"默。随着已接受的 COA 完成并测量其结果，信任度会逐步累积。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
#, python-format
msgid "spread %(spread)s"
msgstr "离散度 %(spread)s"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "▲ trusted"
msgstr "▲ 可信"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "○ not yet"
msgstr "○ 尚未"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Classification"
msgstr "分类"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Set the default report classification and the tier → minimum-role map that "
"gates who can read each tier. A <span class=\"text-cyan\">design floor</"
"span> is enforced server-side — a tier can be tightened but never loosened "
"below its built-in minimum."
msgstr ""
"设置报告的默认密级，以及决定谁能阅读各密级的“密级 → 最低角色”映射。服务端会强"
"制执行一条<span class=\"text-cyan\">设计下限</span> —— 密级只能收紧，绝不能放"
"宽到低于其内置的最低要求。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Default classification"
msgstr "默认密级"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "The tier a report falls back to when its template specifies none."
msgstr "当报告模板未指定密级时所回退到的等级。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid "Tier → minimum role"
msgstr "密级 → 最低角色"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/classification.html
msgid ""
"Restores the default classification and every tier floor to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr "将默认密级和每个密级下限恢复为出厂默认值。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Constraints &amp; thresholds"
msgstr "约束 &amp; 阈值"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Tune the global severity ratios, demand baselines and which constraint "
"providers run. A threshold change re-colours severities on the <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">next snapshot</span> with no deploy. A net-new provider "
"stays disabled until you enable it here."
msgstr ""
"调整全局严重程度比率、需求基线，以及运行哪些约束提供方。阈值变更会在<span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">下一次快照</span>时重新着色严重程度，无需部署。全新的提供"
"方在你于此处启用之前，将始终保持停用。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Global severity ratios"
msgstr "全局严重程度比率"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Constraint providers"
msgstr "约束提供方"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "No constraint providers are registered."
msgstr "尚未注册任何约束提供方。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid "Demand targets"
msgstr "需求目标"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"One per line as <code class=\"text-faint\">key value</code> — e.g. <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>. Leave empty to seed "
"demand from data."
msgstr ""
"每行一条，格式为 <code class=\"text-faint\">key value</code> —— 例如 <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">doctrine:ferox-fleet 22</code>。留空则从数据中自动生成需"
"求。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/constraints.html
msgid ""
"Restores every ratio, provider flag and demand target to the shipped "
"defaults."
msgstr "将所有比率、提供方开关和需求目标恢复为出厂默认值。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Command Intelligence · Scheduled reports &amp; delivery · [FORCA] Command "
"Grid"
msgstr "指挥情报 · 定时报告与投递 · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Scheduled reports &amp; delivery"
msgstr "定时报告 &amp; 投递"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"The weekly briefing generates in the background; delivery is <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">classification-aware</span> and ships <span class=\"text-"
"gold\">disarmed</span> — a director-eyes-only report can never be broadcast "
"to a corp-wide Discord channel (the server refuses that pairing). Nothing "
"leaves the server until you arm a channel and configure its target below."
msgstr ""
"每周简报在后台生成；投递会<span class=\"text-cyan\">识别密级</span>，且出厂状"
"态为<span class=\"text-gold\">未启用</span> —— 仅限董事查阅的报告绝不会被广播"
"到全军团的 Discord 频道（服务器会拒绝这种组合）。在你于下方启用某个渠道并配置"
"其目标之前，不会有任何内容离开服务器。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM enabled — scheduled briefings are narrated. (Without a key they still "
"generate a deterministic report.)"
msgstr ""
"LLM 已启用 —— 定时简报会由 LLM 撰写。（即使没有密钥，也仍会生成确定性报告。）"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"LLM disabled — scheduled briefings still generate the deterministic "
"constraint picture."
msgstr "LLM 已停用 —— 定时简报仍会生成确定性的约束全景。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Scheduled generation"
msgstr "定时生成"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Generate a weekly briefing"
msgstr "生成每周简报"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Monday 12:00 UTC. Deduped against a recent run so a retried beat never "
"double-spends tokens."
msgstr ""
"每周一 12:00 UTC。会与近期的运行去重，因此重试的定时任务绝不会重复消耗 "
"token。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Only announce when binding at/above"
msgstr "仅当约束强度达到或高于此值时才通报"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Suppress delivery of a quiet report with no meaningful constraint."
msgstr "抑制投递没有实质约束的平静报告。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Discord (broadcast)"
msgstr "Discord（广播）"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm Discord delivery"
msgstr "启用 Discord 投递"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Posts a classification-safe summary to every active Discord webhook "
"(configured under In-game Alerts)."
msgstr ""
"向每个已启用的 Discord webhook 发布符合密级要求的摘要（在游戏内警报中配置）。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Broadcast these classifications"
msgstr "广播以下密级"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Only corp-shareable tiers can be broadcast; director/alliance tiers are "
"never offered here."
msgstr "只有可在军团内共享的密级才能广播；董事/联盟密级绝不会在此处提供。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "EVE-mail (targeted to leadership)"
msgstr "EVE-mail（定向发送给领导层）"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Arm EVE-mail delivery"
msgstr "启用 EVE-mail 投递"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Sends an in-game mail to the mains behind the owner tags below. Needs a "
"sender character with the <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</"
"code> scope."
msgstr ""
"向下方负责人标签所对应的主号发送游戏内邮件。需要一个已授予 <code "
"class=\"text-faint\">esi-mail.send_mail.v1</code> 权限范围的发件角色。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Mail these classifications"
msgstr "对这些分类发送邮件"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Targeted mail may carry the sensitive tiers (it is not a broadcast)."
msgstr "定向邮件可以承载敏感等级（它不是广播）。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Sender character id"
msgstr "发件角色 ID"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"A corp character that granted the mail-send scope. Leave blank to disable."
msgstr "一个已授予邮件发送权限范围的军团角色。留空则停用。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid "Recipient owner tags"
msgstr "收件负责人标签"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/notifications.html
msgid ""
"Space- or comma-separated (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">strategic_director</code>). Their mains receive the mail."
msgstr ""
"以空格或逗号分隔（例如 <code class=\"text-faint\">strategic_director</"
"code>）。其主号将收到邮件。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Command Intelligence · Provider &amp; model · [FORCA] Command Grid"
msgstr "指挥情报 · 提供商 &amp; 模型 · [FORCA] Command Grid"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Provider &amp; model"
msgstr "提供商 &amp; 模型"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Pick the runtime model name, output sizing, budgets and call discipline. The "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">API key</span> lives in the environment and is "
"never shown, edited or stored here — only its presence flips the subsystem "
"on."
msgstr ""
"选择运行时模型名称、输出规模、预算与调用规范。<span class=\"text-cyan\">API "
"密钥</span>保存在环境变量中，此处从不显示、编辑或存储 —— 只有它的存在才会开启"
"该子系统。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Enabled — an <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> is present."
msgstr "已启用 —— 已存在 <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code>。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Disabled — set <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> in the "
"environment to enable Command Intelligence."
msgstr ""
"已停用 —— 在环境变量中设置 <code class=\"text-faint\">LLM_API_KEY</code> 以启"
"用指挥情报。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Model name"
msgstr "模型名称"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"The runtime model — overrides the env default (e.g. <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> or <code class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M3</code>)."
msgstr ""
"运行时使用的模型 —— 覆盖环境变量的默认值（例如 <code class=\"text-"
"faint\">MiniMax-M2.7</code> 或 <code class=\"text-faint\">MiniMax-M3</"
"code>）。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Max output tokens"
msgstr "最大输出 token 数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Sized for reasoning plus the answer; raise on a length cut-off. Range 256–"
"65536."
msgstr "需容纳推理过程与答案；若出现长度截断请调高。范围 256–65536。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Temperature"
msgstr "温度"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Sampling temperature, 0–1. Lower is more deterministic."
msgstr "采样温度，0–1。数值越低，结果越确定。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Token budget per report"
msgstr "每份报告的 token 预算"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Hard cap on prompt + completion tokens for a single report."
msgstr "单份报告的提示词 + 补全 token 总量硬上限。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Monthly token ceiling"
msgstr "每月 token 上限"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Safety cap on total tokens spent across all reports in a month."
msgstr "一个月内所有报告消耗 token 总量的安全上限。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Rate limit / hour"
msgstr "速率限制 / 小时"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Reports per hour — backs the breaker counter."
msgstr "每小时报告数 —— 熔断计数器以此为依据。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Repair attempts"
msgstr "修复重试次数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid "Schema / grounding re-prompts on invalid structured output. Range 0–5."
msgstr "结构化输出无效时的 schema / 依据重新提示次数。范围 0–5。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/provider.html
msgid ""
"Restores the model, budgets and call discipline to the shipped defaults."
msgstr "将模型、预算与调用规范恢复为出厂默认值。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Role mappings · Comms access · Admin"
msgstr "角色映射 · 通讯访问 · 管理"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "← Access sync settings"
msgstr "← 访问同步设置"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "External comms access"
msgstr "外部通讯访问"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Role mappings"
msgstr "角色映射"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid ""
"Each row maps a FORCA entitlement to one platform role/group.\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">This is the managed set</strong> — the sync "
"only ever grants or removes roles listed here;\n"
"  anything else on the server is untouchable. A mapping grants when a pilot "
"has the entitlement; it <em>removes</em>\n"
"  on loss only when its mode is <strong class=\"text-ink\">Authoritative</"
"strong>. New mappings stay in dry-run until you confirm them."
msgstr ""
"每一行将一项 FORCA 权限映射到一个平台角色/群组。\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">这就是受管集合</strong> —— 同步只会授予或移除此"
"处列出的角色；\n"
"  服务器上的其他一切都不会被触碰。当飞行员拥有该权限时，映射会授予角色；只有"
"当模式为 <strong class=\"text-ink\">权威</strong> 时，它才会在权限失去时<em>"
"移除</em>角色。新映射在你确认之前始终处于试运行状态。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add a mapping"
msgstr "添加一条映射"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
msgid "Platform"
msgstr "平台"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Entitlement"
msgstr "权限"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. Discord role id"
msgstr "例如：Discord 角色 ID"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "e.g. @Member"
msgstr "例如：@Member"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Target role id / name"
msgstr "目标角色 ID / 名称"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Label (optional)"
msgstr "标签（可选）"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_detail.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/raffle_sources.html
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "模式"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Dry-run"
msgstr "试运行"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Add mapping"
msgstr "添加映射"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Mappings"
msgstr "映射"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "authoritative"
msgstr "权威"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "additive"
msgstr "增量"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "yes"
msgstr "是"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/capsuleer/compare.html
msgid "no"
msgstr "否"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "Remove this mapping? The sync will stop managing that role."
msgstr "移除此映射？同步将不再管理该角色。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/mappings.html
msgid "No mappings yet. Until you add one, the sync manages nothing."
msgstr "尚无映射。在你添加之前，同步不会管理任何内容。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
msgid "Comms access sync"
msgstr "通讯访问同步"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Access sync settings"
msgstr "访问同步设置"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/status.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Linked accounts &amp; ledger"
msgstr "已关联账户 &amp; 账本"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/comms_access/settings.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This subsystem drives external-platform roles from corp membership + RBAC.\n"
"  It ships <strong class=\"text-ink\">inert</strong> and is configured "
"entirely here — no server\n"
"  access needed. To go live: <strong class=\"text-ink\">(1)</strong> enter "
"the Discord credentials,\n"
"  <strong class=\"text-ink\">(2)</strong> enable the feature, <strong "
"class=\"text-ink\">(3)</strong> arm\n"
"  the platform, and <strong class=\"text-ink\">(4)</strong> take its\n"
"  <a href=\"%(mappings_url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">role "
"mappings</a>\n"
"  out of dry-run. The sync only ever touches roles that appear on the Role "
"mappings page."
msgstr ""
"该子系统依据军团成员身份 + RBAC 驱动外部平台角色。\n"
"  它出厂时处于<strong class=\"text-ink\">未激活</strong>状态，并且完全在此处"
