#: templates/industry/mrp.html
msgid ""
"Corp-wide net requirements: every demand source exploded through the build "
"tree and netted once against stock, reservations and in-flight work. Build "
"dates are held to committed manufacturing capacity — slots, skills, "
"blueprints and facilities — and the binding constraint is named. Figures are "
"only as fresh as the syncs and as complete as the opt-in pilots: read this "
"as measured capacity, never total corp capacity."
msgstr ""
"军团范围的净需求：每个需求来源都会沿建造树展开，并一次性对库存、预留和进行中"
"的工作进行净额计算。建造日期锁定到已承诺的制造产能——席位、技能、 blueprint 与"
"设施——并指明约束瓶颈。数据的新鲜度仅取决于同步，完整度仅取决于已选择加入的飞"
"行员：请将其理解为实测产能，而绝非军团总产能。"

#: templates/industry/mrp.html
msgid ""
"Corp-wide net requirements: every demand source exploded through the build "
"tree and netted once against stock, reservations and in-flight work. Dates "
"assume unconstrained industry slots — capacity planning comes in a later "
"phase."
msgstr ""
"全军团净需求：每个需求来源都沿建造树展开，并与库存、预留和进行中的工作做一次"
"净额抵扣。日期假定工业槽位不受限 — 产能规划将在后续阶段推出。"

