#: templates/store/supply_forecast.html
msgid ""
"Demand for doctrine hulls = the composed per-fit demand (loss replacement, "
"upcoming fleet ops, stock targets and manual lines, summed over the hull's "
"fits — hover the rate for the breakdown); other hulls use raw window losses. "
"Supply cost = cheaper of <span class=\"text-cyan\">build</span> (hull at EVE "
"Ref's full job cost — ME-adjusted materials + install fee — or our local "
"estimate when the API can't price it, marked <span class=\"text-cyan\">~est</"
"span>; modules bought at Jita) or <span class=\"text-muted\">import</span> "
"(full fit at Jita), plus jump-freight to staging priced off the corp rate "
"card. Fair sell = the store's own price: Jita sell × markup for doctrine "
"ships and sub-capital hulls, estimated build cost × the class markup for "
"capital and supercapital hulls. Prices are as fresh as the last market sync; "
"capital freight is approximate."
msgstr ""
"Doctrine 船体的需求 = 按配装合成的需求（损失替换、即将进行的舰队行动、库存目"
"标与手动条目，对该船体的各配装求和 —— 将鼠标悬停在速率上可查看明细）；其他船"
"体使用窗口期内的原始损失。供应成本 = <span class=\"text-cyan\">建造</span>"
"（船体按 EVE Ref 的完整作业成本 — 经 ME 调整的材料 + 安装费 — 或在 API 无法定"
"价时采用我们的本地估算，标记为 <span class=\"text-cyan\">~est</span>；模块按 "
"Jita 价购买）与 <span class=\"text-muted\">进口</span>（在 Jita 购入整套配"
"装）两者中较低者，再加上按军团费率卡计价、运往集结点的 jump-freight。公允售"
"价 = 商店自身的价格：doctrine 舰船和 sub-capital 船体按 Jita 卖价 × 加价，"
"capital 和 supercapital 船体按预估建造成本 × 舰级加价。价格新鲜度取决于上次市"
"场同步；capital 运费为近似值。"

